{"tid":2436170,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手貓奴一問-貓咪唔親人可以點算","createTime":"2021-03-07T01:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T15:09:46.000Z","uid":95596,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7f349edd64fd9de7ffa46f6b8be602f446c76e2d","tid":2436170,"uid":95596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:58:02.000Z","msg":"話說屋企人兩個月之前領養咗一隻貓<br />\n貓本身就喺貓舍出世 無咩同人相處嘅經驗<br />\n<br />\n隻貓自己都比較容易緊張同驚青<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時都係餵零食嗰陣先可以偷摸下佢<br />\n我地喺屋企嗰陣佢都可以嘅<br />\n但一有人嚟就好緊張<br />\n<br />\n上次帶佢去絕育已經好驚 <br />\n屋企人捉佢去絕育嗰陣都被佢抓傷 打埋破傷風針<br />\n今次打針已經book咗上門獸醫 希望佢無咁驚<br />\n但係一有人要捉佢 佢就會走 打仗咁款 <br />\n今次佢避獸醫嗰陣都整親自己 隻手仔流咗少少血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想問下有無咩方法可以令佢無咁緊張<br />\n同埋點樣先可以令佢慣有人會摸佢啊<br />\n唔想佢次次睇醫生都打仗咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更唔想佢又整親自己啊"},{"pid":"d2d3220da2ddbaf96bca25168bbb1f5265a94072","tid":2436170,"uid":71343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:14:32.000Z","msg":"玩多d 餵醬個時偷摸下<br />\n我個陣都用左三個幾月時間<br />\n先真係摸到佢"},{"pid":"77d0905e8e264fa49b2f413cdaaeddfd265f2616","tid":2436170,"uid":201414,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:54:28.000Z","msg":"要俾佢知邊個係揸fit果個 冇你=冇野食 冇罐罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452eb0f95524f1d6328c9d79a49f052bc58214c3","tid":2436170,"uid":8948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T02:55:22.000Z","msg":"耐性+愛心，冇其他方法"},{"pid":"0c168434fec88796e1a751af35201dc07ce63b8f","tid":2436170,"uid":182180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T04:15:38.000Z","msg":"試下跟呢2個做<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ST8dlkNGT9I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FST8dlkNGT9I&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=5346febb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ST8dlkNGT9I</a><br 